  rdom VERSION 0.0.3.9000

BUG FIXES

  - Path expansion is now performed on filename argument (see #12)

rdom VERSION 0.0.3

NEW FEATURES

  - New filename argument added to rdom. This allows one to write the HTML string to a file.

IMPROVEMENTS

  - Better error handling
  - Added some basic unit tests

    rdom VERSION 0.0.2

NEW FEATURES

  - Added support for query selectors

    rdom VERSION 0.0.1

NEW FEATURES

  - First version of rdom

MISC

